title: BRIEF-Rubex for Plastic Manufacturing 9-mth loss in line with year ago
text:
BRIEF-Rubex for Plastic Manufacturing 9-mth loss in line with year ago Wed Nov 9, 2016 8:10am GMT 
Nov 9 (Reuters) - Rubex For Plastic Manufacturing Co Sae 
* Nine-month net loss EGP 3.8 million versus net loss EGP 3.8 million year ago 
* Nine-month revenue EGP 82.6 million versus EGP 81.9 million year ago Source: ( bit.ly/2fD49X5 ) Further company coverage:
